{"tid":2378162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環時：一批進口車厘子驗出新冠病毒已銷毀","createTime":"2021-01-24T08:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T15:12:46.000Z","uid":28114,"like":9,"dislike":90,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"10d6780ff1a1110cbfd0289ee07dfabe536f13f3","tid":2378162,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T08:32:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/china-claim-it-found-covid-on-imported-cherries?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Flanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Fchina-claim-it-found-covid-on-imported-cherries%3F&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=46ef57db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/china-claim-it-found-covid-on-imported-cherries?</a><br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》報道，該批車厘子被賣給江蘇省無錫市3個地區的消費者。<br />\n<br />\n該報表示：「目前未知（有病毒車厘子的包裝的）來源國是哪個，但所有同一批次的車厘子已收集起來，準備銷毀。根據無錫梁溪區疫情防疫小組發佈旳聲明，總共199個相關的環境、物品和人員的樣本已被檢測，全部呈陰性結果。」<br />\n<br />\n據報道，該批車厘子在2020年12月18日生產。<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》本月較早前刊登一篇文章，引述「多名水果商人」指澳洲的車厘子因季節因素而質素差，令進口中國的市場份額下跌。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲副總理麥考馬克（Michael McCormack）上周為澳洲車厘子出聲，讚揚它們「紅潤、多汁、豐滿」，「我們無論甚麼地方生產的車厘子都是好的。」<br />\n<br />\n去年10月，專家在青島發現進口急凍鱈魚中發現新冠病毒樣本後，北京一直推動病毒是透過急凍食品進口中國的理論。不過，西方國家多名科學家表示，該理論「純屬臆測」，更傾向相信病毒是在武漢由動物傳給人類。"},{"pid":"cdf0a3d74dce14e42243997fbbdd3a02e5aca2ab","tid":2378162,"uid":19454,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T08:34:06.000Z","msg":"跳舞群組個leader好似叫 車厘子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b348ae3e73a6f455a5366bcb1e2f59e457e5e2b","tid":2378162,"uid":19454,"like":63,"dislike":3,"score":60,"quote":{"pid":"cdf0a3d74dce14e42243997fbbdd3a02e5aca2ab","tid":2378162,"uid":19454,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"c